1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 15]

2
00:00:18,930 --> 00:00:20,889
Ye Zhiqiu, Fifth Concubine of the Zhou Family,

3
00:00:21,330 --> 00:00:24,329
was caught having illicit relations in broad daylight.

4
00:00:24,330 --> 00:00:26,529
She shall be punished according to Zhou family rules:

5
00:00:26,610 --> 00:00:27,929
Death by hanging

6
00:00:28,330 --> 00:00:29,769
as a warning to others.

7
00:00:52,570 --> 00:00:53,289
Don't worry.

8
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:53,889
Last night,

9
00:00:53,890 --> 00:00:55,689
I gave Fifth Concubine some straw ropes.

10
00:00:55,690 --> 00:00:57,089
She wove them into clothes and wore them.

11
00:00:57,210 --> 00:00:58,569
It looks like she's being hanged,

12
00:00:58,570 --> 00:00:59,929
but there's no real danger.

13
00:00:59,930 --> 00:01:00,889
She's wearing it

14
00:01:00,890 --> 00:01:01,609
while being hanged.

15
00:01:02,010 --> 00:01:03,569
Haven't you seen street performances?

16
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:04,209
These are just

17
00:01:04,210 --> 00:01:05,569
tricks to fool people.

18
00:01:07,650 --> 00:01:09,129
Throw her into the pond!

19
00:01:09,330 --> 00:01:10,889
Make sure she's completely dead!

20
00:01:26,570 --> 00:01:27,409
Great!

21
00:01:27,730 --> 00:01:29,209
He's finally come to save Fifth Concubine!

22
00:01:29,210 --> 00:01:30,009
The person you called?

23
00:01:30,010 --> 00:01:30,649
Fifth Concubine

24
00:01:30,650 --> 00:01:32,409
told me to find someone named Yu Shi'an.

25
00:01:32,410 --> 00:01:33,809
He's finally come to save her!

26
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:41,969
You!

27
00:01:44,490 --> 00:01:45,489
These people

28
00:01:45,490 --> 00:01:46,569
don't look like soldiers.

29
00:01:47,210 --> 00:01:48,209
Then who are they?

30
00:01:48,730 --> 00:01:49,609
Who are you?

31
00:01:49,730 --> 00:01:50,729
Let us inform you:

32
00:01:50,810 --> 00:01:51,609
This woman

33
00:01:51,610 --> 00:01:52,809
was saved by Master He.

34
00:01:53,650 --> 00:01:54,889
Master He?

35
00:01:55,090 --> 00:01:56,369
The He family?

36
00:01:56,370 --> 00:01:57,569
Master He?

37
00:01:58,090 --> 00:01:59,089
Could Fifth Concubine

38
00:01:59,250 --> 00:02:01,609
be the daughter he lost among commoners?

39
00:02:01,970 --> 00:02:02,969
Who knows?

40
00:02:14,530 --> 00:02:15,329
Deputy Yu,

41
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,409
why did you take so long?

42
00:02:16,610 --> 00:02:17,529
Where's Fifth Concubine?

43
00:02:17,530 --> 00:02:18,929
She was rescued.

44
00:02:19,250 --> 00:02:19,809
By whom?

45
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:22,489
The mysterious Master He.

46
00:02:45,530 --> 00:02:46,609
Where is this?

47
00:02:47,930 --> 00:02:49,729
Why would Master He save me?

48
00:02:50,210 --> 00:02:52,929
And why drug me and bring me here?

49
00:03:11,930 --> 00:03:12,649
Miss Ye,

50
00:03:12,650 --> 00:03:13,489
you're awake.

51
00:03:13,730 --> 00:03:14,489
May I ask,

52
00:03:15,610 --> 00:03:16,769
where is this place?

53
00:03:17,370 --> 00:03:19,369
This is the princess bedroom at the He family villa.

54
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:21,889
Princess bedroom?

55
00:03:22,130 --> 00:03:22,609
Yes.

56
00:03:22,610 --> 00:03:24,609
Master prepared it especially for you.

57
00:03:24,770 --> 00:03:25,769
What master?

58
00:03:26,530 --> 00:03:27,529
Master He.

59
00:03:28,130 --> 00:03:29,529
The one who's been searching for

60
00:03:29,530 --> 00:03:30,769
his long-lost

61
00:03:31,130 --> 00:03:33,729
illegitimate daughter in Wu County?

62
00:03:34,090 --> 00:03:36,049
So you have heard those rumors too.

63
00:03:36,370 --> 00:03:37,089
But

64
00:03:37,370 --> 00:03:39,249
I can't possibly be his illegitimate daughter.

65
00:03:39,370 --> 00:03:40,329
I have parents.

66
00:03:40,570 --> 00:03:42,649
You'll find out soon enough.

67
00:03:42,650 --> 00:03:44,489
Master is waiting for you downstairs.

68
00:03:44,530 --> 00:03:45,609
I should indeed personally

69
00:03:45,610 --> 00:03:47,409
thank him for saving my life.

70
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:49,729
Then please wear this first.

71
00:03:51,930 --> 00:03:53,249
What is this for?

72
00:03:53,250 --> 00:03:54,529
All guests meeting him

73
00:03:54,530 --> 00:03:55,649
must be blindfolded.

74
00:03:57,090 --> 00:03:59,049
Why is this old man so strange?

75
00:03:59,370 --> 00:04:01,249
Could he have some hidden illness

76
00:04:01,610 --> 00:04:03,409
or undiscovered secret?

77
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:07,609
Careful now.

78
00:04:08,370 --> 00:04:09,049
Careful.

79
00:04:16,450 --> 00:04:17,129
Master.

80
00:04:25,210 --> 00:04:26,449
Are you...

81
00:04:26,650 --> 00:04:27,769
Master He?

82
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:37,249
You...

83
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:38,369
why did you save me?

84
00:04:42,970 --> 00:04:44,209
What do you think?

85
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:45,849
Rumors say

86
00:04:46,650 --> 00:04:47,729
you have been

87
00:04:47,970 --> 00:04:49,449
searching for your illegitimate daughter.

88
00:04:50,930 --> 00:04:51,969
How have I

89
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:53,969
given you that impression?

90
00:04:55,850 --> 00:04:57,729
I deeply appreciate your life-saving grace,

91
00:04:59,530 --> 00:05:00,449
but

92
00:05:00,650 --> 00:05:02,369
I have my own biological parents.

93
00:05:03,450 --> 00:05:04,729
The midwife can attest to this.

94
00:05:07,210 --> 00:05:08,849
I know Wu County quite well.

95
00:05:09,210 --> 00:05:09,969
If

96
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:11,369
you're seeking your daughter,

97
00:05:11,650 --> 00:05:12,969
I could be of assistance.

98
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:18,849
You seem so composed.

99
00:05:20,090 --> 00:05:21,129
Could it be

100
00:05:22,210 --> 00:05:23,729
that you are not looking for a daughter?

101
00:05:25,090 --> 00:05:26,769
Then why save me?

102
00:05:27,330 --> 00:05:27,969
How

103
00:05:28,130 --> 00:05:29,329
could I possibly help you?

104
00:05:30,770 --> 00:05:31,769
In many ways.

105
00:05:32,090 --> 00:05:32,969
Many ways?

106
00:05:35,130 --> 00:05:35,969
Master He,

107
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:37,529
I'm merely a concubine

108
00:05:37,530 --> 00:05:39,369
married into the Zhou household.

109
00:05:39,970 --> 00:05:41,369
What help could I possibly offer you?

110
00:05:49,650 --> 00:05:50,609
Marry me.

111
00:05:53,530 --> 00:05:54,529
What?

112
00:05:55,850 --> 00:05:57,969
When you regain your freedom.

113
00:06:08,330 --> 00:06:09,209
Marry you?

114
00:06:12,730 --> 00:06:13,329
Fine.

115
00:06:15,370 --> 00:06:16,209
But

116
00:06:18,970 --> 00:06:20,329
you must help me eliminate someone.

117
00:06:20,970 --> 00:06:21,769
Who?

118
00:06:25,210 --> 00:06:26,129
This person

119
00:06:27,450 --> 00:06:28,969
took a bullet for me.

120
00:06:30,850 --> 00:06:32,369
Right here on the chest,

121
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:34,369
there's a fatal wound

122
00:06:34,650 --> 00:06:35,729
that hasn't fully healed.

123
00:06:39,850 --> 00:06:41,129
How heartless!

124
00:06:41,970 --> 00:06:43,769
You'd kill someone who saved your life?

125
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:46,209
If I were ruthless,

126
00:06:48,090 --> 00:06:49,209
would you ever give up?

127
00:06:53,850 --> 00:06:54,849
Zhou Yimo?

128
00:07:15,770 --> 00:07:16,969
Why is it you?

129
00:07:19,650 --> 00:07:20,729
How could it be you?

130
00:07:22,850 --> 00:07:24,449
You can have two identities,

131
00:07:25,450 --> 00:07:26,529
but I cannot?

132
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:31,649
Silly you.

133
00:07:32,730 --> 00:07:33,529
You were just about to

134
00:07:34,450 --> 00:07:36,209
call me "Dad".

135
00:07:46,530 --> 00:07:48,649
I could have avoided exposing myself,

136
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:50,209
but for you,

137
00:07:51,130 --> 00:07:52,369
I've cast caution aside.

138
00:07:53,090 --> 00:07:53,969
Without you,

139
00:07:53,970 --> 00:07:55,529
nothing matters.

140
00:09:11,210 --> 00:09:12,769
What is all this nonsense?

141
00:09:13,930 --> 00:09:16,449
Rumors are spreading like wildfire overnight.

142
00:09:17,330 --> 00:09:20,049
Just one night and gossip is everywhere.

143
00:09:21,090 --> 00:09:21,769
I...

144
00:09:21,930 --> 00:09:23,769
I... this family disgrace!

145
00:09:23,770 --> 00:09:25,089
Master, Master!

146
00:09:25,090 --> 00:09:25,889
Please calm down.

147
00:09:25,890 --> 00:09:26,449
Master!

148
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:27,089
Quick!

149
00:09:27,090 --> 00:09:27,889
Take it away and burn it.

150
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:28,449
Yes.

151
00:09:28,530 --> 00:09:29,209
Master!

152
00:09:30,210 --> 00:09:30,769
Master!

153
00:09:34,330 --> 00:09:35,649
Quick, call the doctor for Master!

154
00:09:36,210 --> 00:09:37,569
Yes, Third concubine.

155
00:09:56,090 --> 00:09:56,689
Weren't you

156
00:09:57,530 --> 00:09:59,209
locked in the room?

157
00:09:59,650 --> 00:10:00,809
How did you escape?

158
00:10:01,210 --> 00:10:02,409
There's a secret passage in my room.

159
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:03,769
Only Jinbao

160
00:10:03,770 --> 00:10:04,649
knows about it.

161
00:10:05,450 --> 00:10:06,689
So all these years,

162
00:10:06,930 --> 00:10:08,289
you've been using the playboy persona

163
00:10:08,290 --> 00:10:09,889
to rebuild the He family business?

164
00:10:10,210 --> 00:10:10,769
Yes.

165
00:10:10,930 --> 00:10:11,809
Even Nanxi doesn't know

166
00:10:11,810 --> 00:10:13,049
your true identity?

167
00:10:13,290 --> 00:10:15,569
Every outsider who knows

168
00:10:15,570 --> 00:10:16,889
is a danger to me.

169
00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:22,449
You went to all this trouble

170
00:10:22,930 --> 00:10:24,809
spreading rumors about Master He looking for his illegitimate daughter

171
00:10:26,090 --> 00:10:27,649
just so that one day

172
00:10:28,330 --> 00:10:29,649
you could secretly protect me?

173
00:10:30,210 --> 00:10:30,569
Right.

174
00:10:33,210 --> 00:10:34,049
Protecting you

175
00:10:34,330 --> 00:10:35,649
and having the ability to protect you

176
00:10:35,650 --> 00:10:36,769
are two different things.

177
00:10:36,930 --> 00:10:38,529
The mysterious Master He went to all this trouble

178
00:10:38,930 --> 00:10:39,889
because he believes

179
00:10:39,890 --> 00:10:41,089
he is more capable than Zhou Yimo

180
00:10:41,090 --> 00:10:42,409
of protecting you.

181
00:10:44,530 --> 00:10:45,929
I must return to the Zhou residence now.

182
00:10:47,530 --> 00:10:49,049
Isn't hiding here much better?

183
00:10:49,530 --> 00:10:50,809
The Zhou residence is in complete chaos.

184
00:10:51,170 --> 00:10:52,809
If you go back, Father will surely punish you.

185
00:10:53,530 --> 00:10:54,609
I already said

186
00:10:54,650 --> 00:10:55,529
now is not the best time

187
00:10:55,530 --> 00:10:57,289
for Master He to reveal his identity.

188
00:10:57,530 --> 00:10:58,449
Since that's the case,

189
00:10:58,530 --> 00:11:00,209
I must return to resolve the issues.

190
00:11:00,570 --> 00:11:01,409
Moreover,

191
00:11:01,490 --> 00:11:02,769
finding the murderer hiding

192
00:11:02,890 --> 00:11:04,449
in the residence who killed my sister

193
00:11:05,090 --> 00:11:06,329
is the top priority.

194
00:11:06,330 --> 00:11:07,289
So confident?

195
00:11:08,210 --> 00:11:09,449
But everyone saw it.

196
00:11:10,650 --> 00:11:12,329
How will you prove your innocence?

197
00:11:13,530 --> 00:11:15,089
I don't need to prove my innocence.

198
00:11:16,290 --> 00:11:17,329
I only need to prove

199
00:11:18,290 --> 00:11:19,929
that the person who framed me

200
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:20,809
isn't innocent.

201
00:11:21,330 --> 00:11:22,249
That will be enough.

202
00:11:25,930 --> 00:11:26,489
Master.

203
00:11:26,650 --> 00:11:27,329
What's wrong?

204
00:11:27,450 --> 00:11:28,209
Why so flustered?

205
00:11:28,330 --> 00:11:29,649
The Marshal's men are causing trouble outside.

206
00:11:30,050 --> 00:11:30,809
Claiming

207
00:11:31,090 --> 00:11:32,409
they must see Miss Ye.

208
00:11:41,210 --> 00:11:42,209
That Yu guy.

209
00:11:42,770 --> 00:11:43,209
Yes.

210
00:11:44,210 --> 00:11:45,209
He insists on seeing

211
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:46,209
Miss Ye in person.

212
00:11:47,530 --> 00:11:48,689
He brought a bunch of soldiers.

213
00:11:49,210 --> 00:11:50,049
Tell him

214
00:11:51,330 --> 00:11:53,169
Miss Ye is resting and unavailable.

215
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:54,769
If he doesn't back off,

216
00:11:55,450 --> 00:11:56,449
my hands are tied.

217
00:11:57,090 --> 00:11:57,489
Yes.

218
00:12:00,210 --> 00:12:01,209
It's Yu Shi'an.

219
00:12:02,930 --> 00:12:04,049
He came to rescue me.

220
00:12:04,650 --> 00:12:06,329
Since I'm safe now,

221
00:12:07,170 --> 00:12:07,889
I really should go out

222
00:12:07,890 --> 00:12:08,889
to reassure him.

223
00:12:08,890 --> 00:12:09,529
And thank him.

224
00:12:11,090 --> 00:12:12,929
You expect him to rescue you?

225
00:12:13,690 --> 00:12:15,089
In that situation,

226
00:12:15,090 --> 00:12:17,409
I would have tried anything.

227
00:12:17,530 --> 00:12:19,049
Of course, saving lives is most important.

228
00:12:24,290 --> 00:12:25,649
If you don't hand over Ye Zhiqiu,

229
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:27,489
don't blame me if I force my way in.

230
00:12:28,530 --> 00:12:29,489
Don't do anything reckless!

231
00:12:29,770 --> 00:12:30,929
What's there to argue about?

232
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:37,929
Need help?

233
00:12:40,210 --> 00:12:40,769
No need.

234
00:12:40,930 --> 00:12:42,049
I can handle this myself.

235
00:12:43,210 --> 00:12:43,649
Open the door.

236
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:56,649
Xiaoman.

237
00:12:57,450 --> 00:12:58,649
Master He saved you, right?

238
00:12:59,930 --> 00:13:00,449
Yes.

239
00:13:01,530 --> 00:13:02,569
I'm perfectly fine now.

240
00:13:03,090 --> 00:13:04,089
You don't need to worry about me.

241
00:13:05,770 --> 00:13:07,529
What happened between you and Zhou Yimo at the ancestral hall...

242
00:13:08,810 --> 00:13:09,529
is it true?

243
00:13:09,690 --> 00:13:10,529
No, it's false.

244
00:13:11,450 --> 00:13:12,529
We were framed.

245
00:13:12,810 --> 00:13:13,529
I knew it.

246
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:15,329
Come with me.

247
00:13:15,330 --> 00:13:16,169
Where?

248
00:13:17,650 --> 00:13:19,569
I have the ability to protect you now.

249
00:13:20,490 --> 00:13:21,649
Do you remember those people?

250
00:13:21,930 --> 00:13:22,929
The ones who framed you?

251
00:13:22,930 --> 00:13:23,929
Bullied you?

252
00:13:24,330 --> 00:13:25,449
I will make them pay,

253
00:13:25,450 --> 00:13:26,329
one by one, for you.

254
00:13:26,530 --> 00:13:27,329
I don't need that.

255
00:13:28,930 --> 00:13:29,809
Then what do you want?

256
00:13:29,810 --> 00:13:30,529
Tell me.

257
00:13:31,930 --> 00:13:33,209
I want to return to the Zhou residence.

258
00:13:34,650 --> 00:13:36,209
I still have unfinished business.

259
00:13:36,530 --> 00:13:37,329
You know that.

260
00:13:37,930 --> 00:13:38,929
You want to go back to the Zhou residence?

261
00:13:39,770 --> 00:13:40,809
If you go back...

262
00:13:40,810 --> 00:13:42,489
I have my own way to get away.

263
00:13:43,650 --> 00:13:44,449
I came out

264
00:13:44,810 --> 00:13:46,329
just to let you know I'm safe.

265
00:13:46,810 --> 00:13:48,209
Thank you for saving my life.

266
00:13:48,570 --> 00:13:49,689
Don't worry about me anymore.

267
00:13:51,050 --> 00:13:51,569
Xiaoman.

268
00:13:51,930 --> 00:13:53,049
Please don't go back, okay?

269
00:13:53,450 --> 00:13:53,929
Xiaoman.

270
00:13:54,330 --> 00:13:55,209
I'll investigate for you.

271
00:13:55,450 --> 00:13:56,169
I'll investigate for you.

272
00:13:56,930 --> 00:13:58,209
I can investigate for you.

273
00:13:58,530 --> 00:14:00,089
I can avenge you, do you understand?

274
00:14:00,530 --> 00:14:02,089
I just want you to stay by my side.

275
00:14:02,170 --> 00:14:03,049
Yu Shi'an.

276
00:14:04,930 --> 00:14:06,809
When you were a policeman, you didn't help me.

277
00:14:07,330 --> 00:14:09,569
Money and power have never been my desire.

278
00:14:09,770 --> 00:14:11,209
All I've ever wanted is the truth.

279
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:12,769
What I want

280
00:14:12,770 --> 00:14:14,649
is that worthless thing in your eyes

281
00:14:14,690 --> 00:14:15,769
that justice that belongs

282
00:14:15,770 --> 00:14:16,689
to my sister and me.

283
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:19,769
I beg you,

284
00:14:20,650 --> 00:14:22,169
stop hindering me, okay?

285
00:14:32,450 --> 00:14:33,929
You've fallen for Zhou Yimo.

286
00:14:35,090 --> 00:14:35,649
Haven't you?

287
00:14:45,330 --> 00:14:46,089
No.

288
00:15:21,330 --> 00:15:22,329
Why deny it?

289
00:15:23,770 --> 00:15:25,489
Why won't you admit to our relationship?

290
00:15:26,530 --> 00:15:28,289
Do I mean anything to you at all?

291
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:29,329
Zhou Yimo.

292
00:15:29,810 --> 00:15:30,649
Are you insane?

293
00:15:31,770 --> 00:15:33,489
I'm a person living for revenge.

294
00:15:34,770 --> 00:15:36,449
Even if my heart longs for you,

295
00:15:36,570 --> 00:15:37,929
I must consider the consequences

296
00:15:37,930 --> 00:15:39,409
if this were ever discovered.

297
00:15:39,890 --> 00:15:40,689
Don't forget,

298
00:15:41,690 --> 00:15:43,089
I'm your dad's fifth concubine!

299
00:15:43,690 --> 00:15:45,089
I almost got executed.

300
00:15:55,490 --> 00:15:56,409
Sorry.

301
00:15:56,770 --> 00:15:57,089
I...

302
00:15:57,450 --> 00:15:58,529
I lost my mind.

303
00:16:01,650 --> 00:16:03,329
But seeing how he treated you.

304
00:16:09,170 --> 00:16:09,929
I'll wait for you.

305
00:16:10,930 --> 00:16:11,689
Together,

306
00:16:13,050 --> 00:16:14,049
we'll catch the real killer.

307
00:16:20,410 --> 00:16:22,049
Implementing our plans now

308
00:16:22,450 --> 00:16:23,529
is what matters most.

309
00:16:24,930 --> 00:16:25,889
Our feelings

310
00:16:27,050 --> 00:16:28,329
may yet someday

311
00:16:28,330 --> 00:16:29,329
come to light.

312
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:31,569
But not now.

313
00:16:33,210 --> 00:16:34,289
No promises,

314
00:16:35,570 --> 00:16:36,529
no attachments.

315
00:16:39,450 --> 00:16:40,209
Okay?

316
00:16:41,770 --> 00:16:42,329
Okay.

317
00:16:50,530 --> 00:16:51,529
Why did Master He

318
00:16:52,650 --> 00:16:54,089
save you?

319
00:16:57,090 --> 00:16:58,049
Master He

320
00:16:58,770 --> 00:16:59,489
mistook me for

321
00:16:59,490 --> 00:17:01,289
his long-lost daughter,

322
00:17:01,810 --> 00:17:02,889
so he rescued me.

323
00:17:03,770 --> 00:17:04,929
After the blood test,

324
00:17:05,490 --> 00:17:07,049
he found it wasn't true.

325
00:17:07,530 --> 00:17:09,609
Then why come back?

326
00:17:11,530 --> 00:17:13,489
Want to die again?

327
00:17:14,370 --> 00:17:15,249
I...

328
00:17:16,930 --> 00:17:18,249
just wanted you

329
00:17:18,970 --> 00:17:20,049
to know the truth.

330
00:17:20,050 --> 00:17:21,329
What truth?
